230
00:12:53,427 --> 00:12:55,324
I was livid and looking back,
what I should have done is,

231
00:12:55,412 --> 00:12:58,382
I shouldn't have given them
the nothing option. I should have said,

232
00:12:58,470 --> 00:13:01,440
